"No problem" Quickstrike said snickering.  He scooped up Inferno's 
head in his hand and  grabbed Inferno's body by the ankle with his 
snake head and dragged it along.  When he reached the CR Tank he 
chucked in Inferno's body and held up Inferno's head.
"Well ant boy looks like you got ripped this time.  Ol' Hydras has 
been getting edgy lately."  He tossed in the head along with the 
rest and watched it sink into the machine's white liquid.  He let 
out a yawn.
"I'm beat from al' that walkin'  Time to take me a good ol' nap"  He 
headed back to his quarters and rested.
